snippet.textDisplay: Initially I didn´t want to talk about her plastic surgery, but so many exalting comments about her look made me change my mind. I simply disagree. I like her as a human being, but don´t find results of that plastic surgery natural at all. It looks overdone to me, sorry. Especially that part around and under the chin. Those sharp features do not look real at all for her age. Pause the video at 1:47 on full screen. See how many scars she has? From the ear around the cheek down to and under mouth ( and over her left eyebrow also )... Simply, absence of any ( even miniature ) wrinkles around the eyes, between eyebrows and on forehead will look unreal and plastic on anybody who is 30 years and older.
